NEWS for the R Package Luminescence

Changes in version 0.1.1 (, 2016):

        • new functions:

        • calc_concentrations():

            • add maximum change of concentration in specific level to
              slot 'info'

        • set_ODE():

            • remove 'b', 'temp', 'R' and 'P' from unpacking, because
              these parameters are already stored in parameters.step.

        • set_ODE_LM_OSL():

            • remove 'a', 'b', 'temp', 'R' and 'P' from unpacking,
              because these parameters are already stored in
              parameters.step.

        • simulate_CW_OSL():

            • remove 'RLumModel_ID' from slot info to slot .pid. This
              RLumModel_ID describes the order of the command in the
              sequence.

        • simulate_LM_OSL():

            • remove 'RLumModel_ID' from slot info to slot .pid. This
              RLumModel_ID describes the order of the command in the
              sequence.

        • simulate_RF():

            • remove 'RLumModel_ID' from slot info to slot .pid. This
              RLumModel_ID describes the order of the command in the
              sequence.

        • simulate_TL():

            • remove 'RLumModel_ID' from slot info to slot .pid. This
              RLumModel_ID describes the order of the command in the
              sequence.

        • translate_sequence():

            • add sequence to slot 'info' in returning RLum.Analysis
              object.

Changes in version 0.1.0 (3rd February, 2016):

        • Initial version.

